track_notes:
Park at road barrier on Trefil Road.
Follow Quarry road before leaving and heading for summit.
Deep quarry workings with unprotected steep drops. 
Great care needed in poor visibility.

Approach from the West.
Park at Pontsticill Water Works and follow footpath directly opposite entrance.

Approach from the West.
Park at Pontsticill Water Works and follow footpath directly opposite entrance.
A 75 minute walk up and a 55 minute walk back down. Good parking place roadside just before bridge when coming from the south.
track_title: Slight variation on G4ISJ route from Waterworks
